description: This data file titled “FY 2014 Illinois Operating Budget Detail” contains Fiscal Year 2014 operations budget historical and proposed appropriations for state budgeted entities. The data is sortable by Budgeting for Results categories “Statewide Result Area,” and “Statewide Outcome name.”
